msgid "Aspect Ratio"
msgstr "Raport de Aspect"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:101
msgid ""
"The aspect ratio of the final exported video. 1920×1080 reduces to 16:9. "
"This also takes into account the pixel ratio, for example 2:1 rectangular "
"pixels will affect the aspect ratio."
msgstr ""
"Raportul de aspect al videoclipului final exportat. 1920×1080 se reduce la "
"16:9. Acesta ia în considerare și raportul pixelilor, de exemplu pixelii "
"dreptunghiulari 2:1 vor afecta raportul de aspect."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid "Pixel Ratio"
msgstr "Raportul Pixelilor"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid ""
"The ratio representing pixel shape. Most video profiles use a 1:1 square "
"pixel shape, but others will use rectangular pixels."
msgstr ""
"Raportul care reprezintă forma pixelilor. Majoritatea profilelor video "
"folosesc pixeli pătrați 1:1, dar altele folosesc pixeli dreptunghiulari."

